data.description: Welcome to your tranquil retreat! Step into this meticulously maintained home boasting a SPACIOUS YARD, covered patio, and inviting front porch. Inside, discover a versatile open office space, NEW CARPET, and PAINT throughout. The kitchen is a chef's dream with a black granite island, new cabinets, and a walk-in pantry. Upstairs, find a huge loft, serene bedrooms with ample closets, and a luxurious primary suite. With a Carrier AC system, this home offers comfort year-round. Don't miss the chance to make this your forever home-schedule your showing today!
